node.text:
Welcome back to #GQStaffStyle, a peek inside our coworkers' closets.

Today, @willahbennett reflects on her tie collection: "My father has always been my style north star, and when he gave me a handful of his ties during lockdown, I couldn't stop daydreaming about wearing them into the world. This particular vintage striped tie—tucked neatly into my favorite cricket vest—is a perfect ode to my love of the classic looks he sports so effortlessly."

Read more at the link in bio.

📷: @matteomobilio.
